General.Name: Promimic AB
General.Description: Promimic AB (publ) manufactures, markets, and sells biomaterials for improved osseointegration for orthopedic and dental implants markets. It offers HAnano surface technology that combines various properties that are known to improve osseointegration into one unique surface modification. The company was incorporated in 2004 and is headquartered in Mölndal, Sweden.
